text: Anouk Haars (born 28 December 1994) is a Dutch korfball player. She is a member of KZ/Hiltex and the Netherlands national korfball team. She is a member of the national team since 2020. With the national team she won the gold medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players Category:Sportswomen
